#Create a Credly Badge for your speakers or volunteers
1 request per KCD for either or. Alternatively, you can have a "Contributor" badge that is all encompassing.
Fill out [this Google form](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSex2EhkCNysmK7svQEVeaOlqpsH0fSBe6qoOePRw_WGajZnTw/viewform) to make your request
